{"tid":1909817,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［新界區議員長遠任務］推動棕地土地發展要你哋幫手","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T16:13:34.000Z","uid":20442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfec385fb2374471db309f014b8b1e3a6f74677","tid":1909817,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望你哋記住要做實事，你地要發展18區，撇除黃藍，市民行先！<br />\n照顧老人家要做，研究發展亦要做，抗爭更要做</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，鄉黑同舊區議員一直阻撓政府善用棕地，當然，政府都捨難取易，走去填海、考慮發展郊野公園邊陲，照顧好中國發展商，都懶得照顧哂全部新界鄉黑。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇返好多舊新聞，前立法會議員姚松炎呢篇報道，好想新界區議員心中了然。 鄉黑官對土地發展影響。<br />\n<br />\n//姚松炎認為，有三大來源是解決棕地問題的極大阻礙：「第一個當然就是地主，為了拿到更高的賠償金額，他會一直站在政府的對立面；第二個是黑社會，他們經營的公司多年來違規發展棕地，是用來營利謀生的重要工具；第三個就是區議員。」他解釋，區議員之所以反對收回棕地，通常都是同時身兼地主身份，有的甚至三種身份都有⋯⋯ // <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/335020/%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E7%9F%AD%E8%A6%96%E8%BF%91%E5%88%A9%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99-%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E4%B8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%2F335020%2F%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599-%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E4%25B8%258A&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=5a06ffac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/335020/%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E7%9F%AD%E8%A6%96%E8%BF%91%E5%88%A9%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99-%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E4%B8%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1062804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1062804&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=ad6966af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1062804&h=d6172daa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1062804</a><br />\n<br />\n關於香港到底有幾多棕地，民間研究同土地發展組有兩個講法。<br />\n<br />\n民間研究：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%8F%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25B8%258F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=0c9d7ab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25B8%258F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&h=7eb53cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0-%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%8F%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府土地發展組：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.landforhongkong.hk/tc/supply_analysis/brownfield.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landforhongkong.hk%2Ftc%2Fsupply_analysis%2Fbrownfield.php&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=712b0a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.landforhongkong.hk/tc/supply_analysis/brownfield.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長遠嚟講，你地幫手抗疫，追查冇可疑死屍外，更要做發展社區嘅事，任重道遠，先天下之憂而憂。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass